{"type":"message","id":"2357be41","parentId":"a03d728c","timestamp":"2026-07-02T11:42:12.824Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f6a7f6b3d683435e9c2fa0f6","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 𝗔𝗜 𝗶𝘀𝗻'𝘁 𝗰𝗼𝗺𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗳𝗼𝗿 𝘆𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗷𝗼𝗯.\n\n**Published:** 2026-06-25T15:55:00Z\n**LinkedIn URL:** https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:share:7475939741943898112/\n**Post URN:** urn:li:share:7475939741943898112\n**Format:** text\n**Characters:** 770\n**Pillar:** Technology & AI innovations\n**Image:** (none)\n\n## Post Body\n\n𝗔𝗜 𝗶𝘀𝗻'𝘁 𝗰𝗼𝗺𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗳𝗼𝗿 𝘆𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗷𝗼𝗯.\n\nSomeone using AI is.\n\nThat's the reality right now.\n\nI've watched companies burn 18 months \"exploring AI\"\nwhile competitors shipped in 3 weeks.\nThe gap isn't technology.\nIt's decisiveness.\n\nMost teams think they need:\n→ A bigger budget\n→ More engineers\n→ The perfect strategy\n\nWrong.\nThey need to START.\n\nEvery day you wait is a day someone else\nbuilds the workflow, the agent, the edge.\nThe companies winning right now\naren't smarter or better funded.\nThey just moved.\n\nYou don't need permission.\nYou need execution.\n\nWhat's the ONE thing you'd automate today\nif you had the right tool?\n\n#AI #ArtificialIntelligence #Automation #BusinessGrowth #DigitalTransformation\n\n## Performance\n\n*(populated later by linkedin-analytics)*\n\n- **Impressions:** —\n- **Reactions:** —\n- **Comments:** —\n- **Shares:** —\n- **Last checked:** —\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782992532823}}
{"type":"message","id":"4449a73d","parentId":"2357be41","timestamp":"2026-07-02T11:42:12.825Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6637a3a5fb0b49309328c9d5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 𝗠𝗼𝘀𝘁 𝗰𝗼𝗺𝗽𝗮𝗻𝗶𝗲𝘀 𝗮𝗿𝗲 𝗯𝘂𝗶𝗹𝗱𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗔𝗜 𝗯𝗮𝗰𝗸𝘄𝗮𝗿𝗱𝘀.\n\n**Published:** 2026-06-25T17:40:00Z\n**LinkedIn URL:** https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:share:7475966123159642113/\n**Post URN:** urn:li:share:7475966123159642113\n**Format:** text\n**Characters:** 901\n**Pillar:** Technology & AI innovations\n**Image:** (none)\n\n## Post Body\n\n𝗠𝗼𝘀𝘁 𝗰𝗼𝗺𝗽𝗮𝗻𝗶𝗲𝘀 𝗮𝗿𝗲 𝗯𝘂𝗶𝗹𝗱𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗔𝗜 𝗯𝗮𝗰𝗸𝘄𝗮𝗿𝗱𝘀.\n\nThey pick a tool first.\nThen try to find a problem for it.\n\nThat's backwards.\n\nThe companies winning with AI right now?\nThey start with a PAIN.\nA broken process.\nA manual task eating 20 hours a week.\n\nThen they ask: \"Can AI fix this?\"\n\nNot \"What can ChatGPT do for us?\"\n\nHere's the pattern I see work every time:\n1. Identify one workflow that hurts\n2. Measure the cost of that pain\n3. Build ONE AI agent to kill it\n4. Ship in days, not months\n\nThe tool-first approach?\nThat's how you burn budget and get nothing.\n\nThe problem-first approach?\nThat's how you get ROI in 30 days.\n\nYou don't need an AI strategy.\nYou need ONE problem solved.\n\nWhat's the most painful manual process in your business right now?\n\n#AI #Automation #BusinessGrowth #CTO #AIAgents\n\n## Performance\n\n*(populated later by linkedin-analytics)*\n\n- **Impressions:** —\n- **Reactions:** —\n- **Comments:** —\n- **Shares:** —\n- **Last checked:** —\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782992532825}}
